Package: crsuggest
Type: Package
Title: Obtain Suggested Coordinate Reference System Information for Spatial Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Kyle", family = "Walker", 
           email="kwalkerdata@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Uses data from the EPSG Registry to look up suitable coordinate reference 
    system transformations for spatial datasets in R.  Returns a data frame with CRS codes
    that can be used for CRS transformation and mapping with coord_sf() in ggplot2.  
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  sf,
  dplyr,
  purrr,
  mapview,
  lwgeom
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
